THIRD-PARTY REFERENCES
================================================================================

This is a clean-room implementation written from a self-contained binary-format
specification. No third-party source code is incorporated. The following
open-source projects and public documentation were consulted as references /
cross-checks for the publicly-documented CASC, TACT, TVFS, BLTE and Diablo IV
SNO formats, and are credited with gratitude. See THIRD-PARTY.md for details.

  - WoW-Tools/CascLib (TOM_RUS)            — MIT — CASC/TACT/TVFS/BLTE behaviour
  - Dakota628/d4parse                      — Diablo IV SNO / .tex format notes
  - DiabloTools/d4data                     — combined-meta bundle (0x44CF00F5)
  - HoldMyBeer-gg/rustydemon               — Diablo IV texture format notes
  - alkhdaniel/diablo-4-string-parser      — Diablo IV .stl StringList notes
  - wowdev.wiki (TACT/CASC community docs) — protocol documentation
